Title: First Squad: The Moment of Truth
Original title : First Squad: The Moment of Truth
Year: 2009
Genre: Fantasy, Adventure , Cartoon
Directed by Yoshiharu Asino
Voice artist Elena Chebaturkina Mikhail Tikhonov, Damir Eldar , Lyudmila Shuvalov , Irina Savina, Sergei Eismann , Alexander Gruzdev , Rudolf Pankov, Nikita Prozorovskii Olga Golovanov

About the film:
Cartoon action unfolds in 1942. Squad pioneer heroes comes to grips with the Nazi occupiers and ghosts knights of the Livonian Order , summoned from the underworld Nazi magicians of the infamous organization Ahnenerbe . Of course , the main characters - not just the pioneers . They have been trained in the Sixth Division of the Office of Naval Intelligence .
